Ma's arent that gimp in pvp (mass-pvp : yes) . There are some proff's we ma's can kick. For example a doc : a doc without any outside buffs (that would be Mark) they dont deal out alot of dmg (exept when they crit) so all u need to kill a doc is just alot of nano. When a doc dont have any nano left, he/she is fucked! And the other proff that we can take , is a agent (well, not if he go fp trader ;) . Agent have one thing they can do to kill ya, they'r crit buff but that only lasts for 5secs or something, and when they use that u will need a decent FoL. Use it and the agent stands there looking like a fried chicken. But back to the case. Ac isn't that important, look more at the bonus. Max hp is one of the major bonuses u should look for. and when u get over 160 all abilites should be maxed<br>
